actiuni/interogari
-> adaugare client // addClient(Client client)
-> stergere client // deleteClient(Client client)
-> adaugare credit // createLoan(Float value, Currency currency, Duration duration)
-> stergere credit daca sunt platite ratele // payLoan(Loan loan)
-> calculare rata pentru credit nou //
-> calcularea platii tuturor ratelor // calculateAllLoans(Currency newCurrency)
-> plata rate // payLoan(Loan loan)
-> amanare rate // postponeLoan()
-> informatii despre ratele curente // getInformation()
-> conversia cursului valutar // calculateExchangeRate(Currency oldCurrency, Currency newCurrency)
-> conversia ratelor in alta valuta // changeLoanCurrency(Currency newCurrency)

obiecte
-> persoana // class Person
-> client // class Client
-> banca // class Bank
-> credit // class Loan
-> durata credit // class Loan
-> rata // class Rate
-> curs valutar // class CurrencyConverter
-> valuta // abstract class Currency

nume fisier: history.csv